  <name>Tasks</name>
  <name xml:lang="cs">Úkoly</name>
  <summary>Get things done</summary>
  <summary xml:lang="cs">Dokončete, co jste začali</summary>
  <summary xml:lang="uk">Доводьте справи до кінця</summary>
  <description>
    <p>A simple task management app, reaching across the cosmos to help you get things done</p>
    <p xml:lang="cs">Jednoduchá aplikace pro správu úkolů, která vám pomůže dokončit, co jste začali</p>
    <p xml:lang="uk">Від одного завдання — до космічного порядку. Простий менеджер завдань, що приборкує будь-який хаос.</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Exceptional performance and responsiveness.</li>
        <li xml:lang="cs">Výjimečný výkon a rychlá odezva.</li>
        <li xml:lang="uk">Виняткова продуктивність і швидкий відгук.</li>
        <li>Effortless keyboard shortcut support.</li>
        <li xml:lang="cs">Bezproblémová podpora klávesových zkratek.</li>
        <li xml:lang="uk">Зручна підтримка сполучень клавіш.</li>
        <li>Expressive emoji integration.</li>
        <li xml:lang="cs">Expresivní integrace emoji.</li>
        <li xml:lang="uk">Виразна інтеграція Emoji.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <branding>
    <color type="primary" scheme_preference="light">#eaeaff</color>
    <color type="primary" scheme_preference="dark">#280c4b</color>
  </branding>
  <icon type="remote" height="256" width="256">https://raw.githubusercontent.com/edfloreshz/tasks/master/res/icons/hicolor/scalable/apps/dev.edfloreshz.Tasks.svg</icon>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">dev.edfloreshz.Tasks.desktop</launchable>
  <releases>
    <release version="0.2.3" date="2026-05-04">
        <description>
            <p>Trash &amp; Favorites</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Added Trash, a special list for managing deleted tasks</li>
                <li>Added support for restoring and permanently deleting tasks from Trash</li>
                <li>Added Favorites, a special list that collects your favorite tasks</li>
                <li>Added a favorite toggle button to tasks</li>
                <li>Added "Show Favorites" and "Hide Completed" toggles in Settings</li>
                <li>Sort menu items now display a checkmark when selected</li>
                <li>Fixed a bug with configuration persistence</li>
            </ul>
        </description>
    </release>
    <release version="0.2.2" date="2026-05-04">
        <description>
            <p>Quality of life improvements</p>
            <ul>
                <li>When deleting a task, a banner is shown with an option to undo.</li>
                <li>It is now possible to delete a task from the edit pane.</li>
                <li>The edit pane now displays tasks created and completed dates.</li>
                <li>The new task input is now focused on app start and when selecting or creating a list.</li>
                <li>Dialog inputs are selected when creating or renaming a list.</li>
                <li>Search input is selected when opened, it also handles discard events.</li>
            </ul>
        </description>
    </release>
    <release version="0.2.1" date="2026-05-03">
        <description>
            <p>Bug fixes and improvements</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Fixed a layout invalidation issue with sub-tasks.</li>
                <li>Fixed a bug causing due dates to revert to their previous value.</li>
                <li>Fixed a bug where lists were deleted from the filesystem but the change wasn't reflected in the UI.</li>
                <li>Menu options are now disabled when no list is selected.</li>
                <li>Added migration code to handle the legacy store schema.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Internationalization improvements</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Added a new translation key to support displaying creation timestamps.</li>
                <li>Updated French, Czech, and Ukrainian translations.</li>
            </ul>
        </description>
    </release>
    <release version="0.2.0" date="2025-05-27">
        <description>
            <p>Powerful new features! 🚀</p>
            <ul>
                <li>✨ <em>Sub-tasks support</em></li>
                <li>🔍 <em>Search functionality</em></li>
                <li>📊 <em>Task sorting</em></li>
                <li>🎨 <em>Expanded icon library</em></li>
                <li>🌍 <em>Enhanced internationalization</em></li>
                <li>🔧 <em>Better task management</em></li>
                <li>⌨️ <em>Improved keyboard shortcuts</em></li>
                <li>🎯 <em>Hide completed tasks</em></li>
                <li>📋 <em>Enhanced export options</em></li>
                <li>🐛 <em>Bug fixes and performance improvements</em></li>
            </ul>
        </description>
    </release>
    <release version="0.1.1" date="2024-11-06">
        <description>
            <p>Text editor for notes 🎉</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Notes now has a multiline text editor</li>
                <li>The window has a border</li>
                <li>The theme is now synced with COSMIC</li>
                <li>The about page has been revamped</li>
            </ul>
        </description>
    </release>
    <release version="0.1.0" date="2024-07-02">
        <description>
            <p>Initial release! 🎉</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Organize tasks into lists</li>
                <li>Rest your eyes with dark mode</li>
                <li>Manage tasks with ease using keyboard shortcuts</li>
                <li>Export tasks to Markdown</li>
            </ul>
        </description>
    </release>
  </releases>
